snippet.title: Shadow Of The Wool Ball - Doom Mod Madness
snippet.description:
Quite possibly one of the most adorable Doom mods i've ever played, Shadow of the Wool Ball puts you in the shoes of a heroic hedgehog (no, not Sonic) in search of his kidnapped girlfriend. Can he prevail against the evil might of the kitty empire?

SHADOW OF THE WOOL BALL
